    "ideation": "The lotion bottle animation focuses on the tactile sensation of viscous liquid and the mechanical cycle of a pump. The 'acting' personifies the bottle as a soothing provider. The arc follows a cycle of anticipation, a sudden mechanical 'pump' squeeze where the lids narrow and the mouth wave compresses, followed by the 'dispensing' of smooth, silky fluid. The mouth wave is the key: it transitions from a stiff line to a slow, thick, rolling sine wave to represent the lotion flowing out. Colors move from a clean, clinical white/teal to a soft, moisturizing lavender to evoke a sense of calm and relief.",
